Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:06.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}心与心远离　呼唤遥远真实
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:18.17,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,500)}天边卷云翻滚　眺望同一缕光明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让直布罗陀也协助调查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.25,0:00:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人侦察机没用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.89,0:00:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要的是详细情报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么不知道有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.03,0:00:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里来的情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似使用的是独眼巨人系统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量埋藏在地下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但据称安然无事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命他提交详细报告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以艾琳·卡纳巴为首的几名议员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,态度非常强硬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们要求知道事态真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们可能打算召开临时议会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.35,0:00:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之命令残存部队撤回卡本塔里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忙中出错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在需要的是冷静客观的分析
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵一伙的去向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未查明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑路线似乎安排得非常周密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会比想象中更费时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.24,0:01:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让司法局出面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕包括卡纳巴在内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有与克莱茵来往密切的议员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵串通间谍盗取机体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.08,0:01:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后与其父逃亡 至今去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骤雨作战的攻击目标被提前泄漏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子都能看懂这其中的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵才是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.04,0:01:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们难道想来追究我的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡纳巴她们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.97,0:01:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们那些人…不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是她们在包庇逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:01:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉议长阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况了解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…不 我无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝会串通间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种荒谬的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是工厂监控摄像头的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后自由就被盗走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是铁证如山谁会怀疑到她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论你怎么想 这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵已经不再是你的婚约者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还未对外公布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经是犯了叛国罪的在逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是前往夺回被盗取的X-10A自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死其驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并消灭所有与之接触过的人和设施
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到工厂领取X-09A正义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备就绪后立即开始任务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无法夺回机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要彻底摧毁自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是消灭所有有接触的人和设施吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-10A自由和X-09A正义是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载有反中子干扰的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反中子干扰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:05:02.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}以正义之名
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.29,0:05:02.05,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}以正义之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT说过放弃所有核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了获胜又重新需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种能源
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务事关重大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少想没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔也很喜欢她的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼科尔的事很对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也懂 这就是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹你替他报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.89,0:05:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就像你和尼科尔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,众多年轻人在战场上抛头颅撒热血
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还会有人甘心背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲已经够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才下决心批准反中子干扰器的研制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始最终启动测试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F6检测人员终端上线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西要是落入地球人手里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们又会兴高采烈地挥舞起核武
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何必须避免那种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳·卢·克鲁泽队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想把我这个哀悼团代表所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成为战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你了 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是 基拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 到底上哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 真的不是幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛 卡兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们有许多话要谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有许多事想问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去扎夫特那儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 但我不是扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 也不再是地球军了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 这我们稍后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该拿它怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您在说维护和补给的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时还不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体搭载有反中子干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反中子干扰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那东西是核动力的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿给你搞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要收集机体数据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拒绝 然后离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想夺走它 就算与你们为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会保护它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:42.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为它的驾驶者 这是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我吩咐他们别碰机体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这花 是我第一次登台演唱的剧院的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为纪念种下的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是作战计划？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总部知道扎夫特的攻击目标是阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定是很早以前就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不可能在地下安放那么多独眼巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西格尔·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被萨拉蒙在鼓里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骤雨作战的目标不是巴拿马
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿拉斯加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大天使号 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫小姐今后打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于中子干扰和磁场的阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在通讯不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时修修补补 自己去巴拿马？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会受欢迎吗 我们知道得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰未经许可离开战列
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会落得个临阵脱逃的罪名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大部队也是军事法庭伺候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又多了条罪状
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 不知道自己是在为了什么战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为结束这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛硫小姐认为应该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:12:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要找到真正必须与之战斗的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去奥布？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 已经没谁愿意回军队了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪毙是板上钉钉的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与之战斗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 等会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太舍得关掉电源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是知道的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实对基拉根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在阿拉斯加调走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和巴基露露中尉 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有弗拉戈少校一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校是回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但中尉和芙蕾走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你死了 特别难过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着回来 打从心底里高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不一样！ 你是和我不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次 每次 每次看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都让我自卑的无地自容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛也有跟我不一样的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事你做不到 或许我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没能做到的事 你却做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:52.35,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\fs32}（白康乃馨剧院）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.07,0:15:01.31,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\fs32}（拉克丝·克莱茵）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:13.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}夜在波光中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:27.57,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}哀愁静静伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:34.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}翠绿的海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:42.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}鲜美的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:49.60,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}若能一直守候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:56.50,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}带着纯洁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.93,0:16:16.23,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}暗海与天空彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:30.06,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}有处与世无争的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}是谁告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:45.33,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}谁却也无法抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:52.53,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}或者它只存在于人们心中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:17:07.96,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平息浊流　滋润大地万物的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:14.80,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}现在又在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.15,0:17:21.39,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}一定只有自己亲手去获得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:29.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}一定　会有　一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}拉克丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为被杀所以去杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}因为杀所以被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这样最后真的能和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小粉红
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你把它带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释一下 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来这里之前 难道没有听过解释吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些都是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你串通间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么干那种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有串通过什么间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是将一把新剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给了基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉现在需要它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且配得上它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么 基拉他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你杀了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 基拉还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什么企图？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样满口谎话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…那家伙不可能还活着！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马鲁奇奥导师把他带到我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也告诉了我 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言已经不值得相信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你亲眼目睹的事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.56,0:19:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上 在久违的PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么也没有看到是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰相信为之而战的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是收获的勋章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是父亲大人的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也许还会成为你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌人的话 向我开枪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.07,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是前婚约者 果然知根知底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是在逃的叛国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已情况下可以格杀勿论
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算包庇她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了吧 拉克丝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马鲁奇奥导师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经安全离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.93,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你把小粉红带来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉就在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见面聊聊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A55警报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辐射量正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线清空 全站点出击许可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.88,0:21:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒数T200开始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰相信为之而战的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.36,0:21:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见面聊聊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老朋友
